#: src/2166-impl-only-use.md:9
msgid ""
"The `use …::{… as …}` syntax can now accept `_` as alias to a trait to only "
"import the implementations of such a trait."
msgstr ""

#: src/2166-impl-only-use.md:12
msgid "Motivation"
msgstr "動機"

#: src/2166-impl-only-use.md:15
msgid ""
"Sometimes, we might need to `use` a trait to be able to use its methods on a "
"type in our code. However, we might also not want to import the trait symbol "
"(because we redefine it, for instance):"
msgstr ""

