msgid "// `Trait` is in scope too\n"
msgstr ""

#: src/2166-impl-only-use.md:106
msgid ""
"In the case where the symbol is not a _trait_, it works the exact same way. "
"However, a warning must be emitted by the compiler to state the unused "
"import (as types don’t have `impl`!)."
msgstr ""

