msgid "Drawbacks"
msgstr ""

#: src/2166-impl-only-use.md:119
msgid ""
"This RFC tries to solve a very specific problem (when you _must_ alias a "
"trait use). It’s just a nit to make the syntax more _“rust-ish”_ (it’s very "
"easy to think such a thing would work given the way `_` works pretty much "
"everywhere else)."
msgstr ""

